From a8e553b9e99369aacf9ed20b26d4359e8280c539 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Juan Manuel Lopez Carrillo <juanmanuellopezcarrillo@gmail.com>
Date: Sat, 18 Jul 2026 06:01:56 +0200
Subject: [PATCH 123/131] config: activar PCIE_SUN55I_RC=y + AW_INNO_COMBOPHY=y
 (PCIe T527)

Controlador PCIe RC sunxi y combo PHY Inno built-in, como el resto del
bring-up de plataforma, para que con NVME=m (ya activo) el orden de
probe sea trivial. Arrastra los simbolos derivados del olddefconfig.

Co-Authored-By: Claude Fable 5 <noreply@anthropic.com>
---
 .config | 9 +++++++++
 1 file changed, 9 insertions(+)

diff --git a/.config b/.config
index c7dd87893..8ce33489e 100644
--- a/.config
+++ b/.config
@@ -1789,6 +1789,14 @@ CONFIG_PCI_EPF_TEST=m
 
 CONFIG_PCI_PWRCTRL=y
 CONFIG_PCI_PWRCTRL_SLOT=y
+
+#
+# PCIe Drivers
+#
+CONFIG_PCIE_SUN55I_RC=y
+# CONFIG_PCIE_SUN55I_NONE is not set
+# end of PCIe Drivers
+
 # CONFIG_CXL_BUS is not set
 # CONFIG_PCCARD is not set
 # CONFIG_RAPIDIO is not set
@@ -8102,6 +8110,7 @@ CONFIG_PHY_SUN4I_USB=y
 CONFIG_PHY_SUN6I_MIPI_DPHY=m
 # CONFIG_PHY_SUN9I_USB is not set
 # CONFIG_PHY_SUN50I_USB3 is not set
+CONFIG_AW_INNO_COMBOPHY=y
 
 #
 # PHY drivers for Broadcom platforms
